Doris - Did You Give the World Some Love Today, Baby
Original LP 1970, tracks 1-12
CD 1996, with bonus tracks 13-22 (The Pop Years)

Doris Svensson, billed as Doris, is a former Swedish pop singer. Doris is
best known for her solo album, eclectic pop, rock and funk
Did You Give the World Some Love Today Baby recorded in 1970.
